playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/d236c28f3c239834e18dcdb0640ceffd.poster.avif?t=1688064012\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/d236c28f3c239834e18dcdb0640ceffd.webm?t=1688064012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/f83bbddb4da73b5cc56fb365c96e23aa.webp?t=1688064012\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Easy to learn but difficult to master, most levels are 15 seconds or less. Discovering hidden paths may help you shave seconds off your best run but most of the time, you'll be racing for milliseconds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/727a1f900192c6797bd8d16b2d73829e.poster.avif?t=1688064012\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/727a1f900192c6797bd8d16b2d73829e.webm?t=1688064012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/727a1f900192c6797bd8d16b2d73829e.mp4?t=1688064012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/5e901f8dda0e5c37da6e8ec8497730e9.webp?t=1688064012\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>Activate the Chrono Echo to load your best run and compete head to head with the past!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307920/extras/cecd5c801ae59fe42b9e5aa782d5f924.po